Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:11.17,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{We'll be heading south of Mismede,}Tujuannya selatan Mismede.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:15.59,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{past the Sea of Trees to the \NBurning Kingdom of Sandora,}Negara yang terletak setelah lautan \Npepohonan, Kerajaan Sandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.77,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{and then to the Rabbi Desert \Nsoutheast of there!}Lalu Gurun Rabbi \Nyang ada di tenggara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:21.10,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{I heard that long ago, \Nthere were six stone pillars}Dulu, di reruntuhan kuno bawah gurun ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:24.77,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{embedded with spellstones lying \Nwithin ancient ruins in that desert!}... katanya tertanam \Nenam pilar batu sihir, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:29.05,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Though apparently those ruins have \Nnow been swallowed up by the desert.}Meski sekarang reruntuhannya \Nsudah tertimbun gurun pasir, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:30.99,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Good for you.}Baguslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:34.42,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{What's with that completely \Ndisinterested reaction?}Reaksi seolah sangat \Ntidak tertarik macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:36.49,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{You're not thinking you can \Njust go poke your head in,}Kamu tidak berniat lihat-lihat ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:39.49,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{take a look, and come right back home, are you?}... lalu langsung pulang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:40.71,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{How did you know?}Kok bisa tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:42.67,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Naughty underwear.}Dalaman seksiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:44.21,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I get it, okay?!}Ngerti, kok!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:45.17,Main,Elze,0,0,0,,{Underwear?}Dalaman?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:47.20,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,{What is she talking about?}Lagi ngobrolin apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:49.38,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{It's nothing! Nothing at all!}Bukan apa-apa! \NBukan apa-apa ....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:52.16,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{I just hope it's the Library. Right?}Semoga, sih, perpustakaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:54.92,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{I don't think we need to \Nwork that hard to find it...}Tidak usah seniat itu nyarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:57.73,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{But I am curious about the extermination}Meski begitu, aku penasaran ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:00.60,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{of an ancient civilization \Nat the hands of the Phrase.}... dengan peradaban kuno \Nyang dihancurkan Phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:03.20,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{It's all well and good if \NI'm just overthinking it,}Semoga cuma terlalu kupikirkan, sih, tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:07.83,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{but there's a chance we may need the power \Nof Babylon if the worst comes to pass,}saat situasi memburuk, bisa \Njadi harus pinjam kekuatan Babylon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:11.28,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{and I refuse to regret not \Nacting before it's too late.}Aku nggak mau nyesal \Nkalau itu sudah terjadi, soalnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:13.73,Main,Kohaku,0,0,0,,{Master, look at that!}Tuan, coba lihat itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:16.39,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{A Phrase?!}Phrase?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:22.75,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{What do we do?}Gimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:25.09,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{We can't just leave them be.}Jelas tak bisa diabaikan, 'kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:03.14,ep-title-chapter,Screen,0,0,0,,{Chapter 2}Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:03.14,ep-title-name,Screen,0,0,0,,{The Stranded and the Workshop}Terdampar dan Lokakarya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.70,Main,Linze,0,0,0,,{This way, while you can!}Ayo ke sini sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.59,Main,Elze,0,0,0,,{Hide behind here.}Sembunyi di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.31,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Wh-Who are you?}Ka-Kamu siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:26.37,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,{Touya-dono!}Tuan Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.54,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,{Send me above it with Gate!}Pakai Gate untuk \Nmengirimku ke atasnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.67,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Got it!}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.72,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,{Prepare yourself!}Bersiaplah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.55,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,{It didn't work?}Tidak mempan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.47,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Yae?!}Yae!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.35,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,{Touya-dono! Use Gate!}Tuan Touya, pakai Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.56,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,{My apologies.}Mohon maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.02,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Everyone, spread out!}Semuanya, mundur!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.61,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{You've got to be kidding me!}Bercanda, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.91,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{We'd be goners if we took a blow from that.}Kena satu tembakan saja bisa fatal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:04.39,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{I wondered who it was. It's you, Touya?}Kukira siapa, ternyata Touya, toh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:06.61,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Ende?!}Ende?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.60,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{Hey, long time no see.}Yo, lama tak jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.04,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{I sensed the Phrase and came out here,}Karena merasakan keberadaan \NPhrase, aku pun ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.09,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{but I didn't expect to run into you.}Tak kusangka bisa bertemu denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.09,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{You know about the Phrase?}Kamu tahu mengenai Phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:19.47,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{I do.}Tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:24.14,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{Though I'm surprised a Standard \NPhrase has made it this far.}Meski tak kusangka \NKelas Menengah sampai datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:27.10,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{I guess the World Barrier \Nis already at its limit.}Sepertinya Penghalang Dunia \Nsudah mencapai batas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:27.77,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.03,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{Anyway, hang on a sec.}Yah, tunggu sebentar, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.06,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{I'll take care of that first.}Aku akan mengurusnya dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:42.79,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{What?!}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.03,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{What the heck did you do?}Kamu apain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:54.05,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{Nothing.}Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:58.92,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{I just destroyed it by hitting it with \Nmagic attuned to its natural frequency.}Hanya hancurkan pakai sihir yang \Ndisesuaikan dengan frekuensi alaminya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.15,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Ende...}Ende.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:03.10,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{You just mentioned a "World Barrier," right?}Tadi kamu bilang \N"Penghalang Dunia", 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.39,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{What is that?}Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:08.92,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{It's basically a net that keeps \Nforeign things out of this world.}Semacam jaring yang melindungi agar \Nbenda asing tak masuk ke dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:11.60,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{Though it looks like it's starting to fray.}Tapi, sepertinya mulai retak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:14.36,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{This thing probably slipped through it, too.}Mungkin dia juga lolos dari situ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:18.93,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{Though it's just a minion that \Nonly acts to achieve its goal.}Meski cuma keroco yang hanya \Nbergerak untuk tuntaskan tujuan, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.07,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Goal?}Tujuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:23.10,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{To find the Phrase's sleeping king.}Mencari raja Phrase yang tertidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.83,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{It's the same goal I have.}Tujuannya sama denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.05,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{I need to get going now.}Aku harus pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.93,Main,Ende,0,0,0,,{Farewell, Touya. I hope we meet again.}Dah, Touya. \NSemoga ketemu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:31.75,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.21,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{The Phrase's king?}Raja Phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.43,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{That hits the spot.}Selamat ....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:46.20,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Touya, you have my gratitude.}Tuan Touya, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.77,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{You saved us.}Berkatmu, kami selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:50.54,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{I'm Rebecca, an adventurer.}Aku Rebecca, petualang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.89,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{An adventurer?}Petualang?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:55.24,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{You all seem awfully lightly \Narmed for adventurers.}Meski begitu, perlengkapan \Nkalian sedikit, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.86,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Those girls aren't adventurers.}Mereka bukan petualang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:01.32,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{The things around their necks \Nare Enslavement Collars.}Yang terpasang \Ndi lehernya ialah Kalung Budak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.22,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Enslavement Collars?}Kalung Budak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.20,Main,Rebbecca,0,0,0,,{Once it's on you, that's it.}Sekali dipasang, tak bisa lepas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.07,Main,Rebbecca,0,0,0,,{It's a magic item that makes \Nyou unable to defy orders,}Alat sihir yang membuat mereka ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.63,Main,Rebbecca,0,0,0,,{even when you're treated as property.}... tak bisa menentang perintah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:11.18,Main,Rebbecca,0,0,0,,{Attempting to remove it \Nwill inflict intense pain}Akan sangat sakit \Nsaat dilepas dengan paksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.42,Main,Rebbecca,0,0,0,,{that can lead to death at its worst.}Parahnya bisa sampai mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:15.06,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{That's awful.}Tidak manusiawi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:18.16,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Yeah, it's truly cruel.}Iya, sungguh kejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:21.12,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Only the person who placed \Nit on them can remove it,}Hanya bisa dilepas oleh \Norang yang memakaikan, tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.63,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{but that person is already dead.}orangnya sudah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.48,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Once we heard about their situation,}Saat dengar kondisinya, kami ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.87,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{we decided to help them flee the country.}... berniat bantu mereka untuk kabur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:33.47,Main,Logan,0,0,0,,{We thought we might be able to find a way\Nto remove the collars somewhere else.}Kami kira bakal nemu cara \Nuntuk lepaskan kalungnya di tempat lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:36.45,Main,Logan,0,0,0,,{Anyway, pathetic as it is, \Nwe got lost and stranded,}Yah, sayangnya kami tersesat ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.61,Main,Logan,0,0,0,,{and then that monster attacked us, too.}... dan diserang monster yang tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.03,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Hey, Touya.}Hei, Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:44.22,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I think I might be able to \Nremove those collars.}Mungkin aku bisa melepas kalungnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:45.36,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,{What?!}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:50.99,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Apport.}Apport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.08,Main,Will,0,0,0,,{Th-The collar is off!}Ka-Kalungnya lepas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:59.68,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Apport! Apport! Apport! \NApport! Apport! Apport!}Apport! Apport! Apport! \NApport! Apport! Apport!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.80,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{What are you going to do now?}Setelah ini mau 'gimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:07.70,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Removing the collars still \Ndoesn't wipe their records.}Meski kalungnya berhasil lepas, \Nbukan berarti statusnya berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:10.60,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Staying in Sandora would \Nbring them nothing but trouble.}Bakal repot kalau tinggal di Sandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.18,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{So we're still planning to take \Nthem to some other nation...}Sepertinya harus \Ndibawa ke kerajaan lain ....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.34,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{In that case, would you like to go to Belfast?}Kalau begitu, mau ke Belfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:17.98,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:18.94,Main,Logan,0,0,0,,{Who are you?}Kamu siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.61,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you.}Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:25.17,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{I am Yumina Urnea Belfast, \Ndaughter of Tristwyn Urnes Belfast,}Putri raja Tristwyn Urnes \NBelfast dari Kerajaan Belfast,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.95,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{King of the Kingdom of Belfast.}Yumina Urnea Belfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:28.69,Main,Others,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:31.29,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{I heard everything about your situation.}Aku sudah dengar semua \Nmengenai kondisi kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:35.15,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{My country would be able to take you in.}Kerajaanku bisa menerima kalian, jadi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.79,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{Would you like to come?}bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:42.42,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{U-Um, p-please, if we can!}A-Anu, mohon bantuannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.29,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{Then let's send everyone to Belfast.}Kalau begitu, akan \Nkukirim kalian ke Belfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.89,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{Touya, if you would?}Touya-san, tolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:03.51,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Rebecca-san and the others can \Nlive in my house for a while,}Rebecca-san dan yang lain sementara \Nwaktu akan tinggal di rumahku,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:06.61,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{and figure out what their \Nfuture looks like later.}lalu tindakan selanjutnya \Nakan dipikirkan nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:09.82,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Now, shall we continue on to the ruins?}Nah, ayo lanjut cari reruntuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.06,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Before we do that...}Sebelum itu ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.97,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Who was that boy earlier?}... siapa cowok tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.50,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{What's your relationship?}Hubungannya apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:19.10,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{O-Oh, right.}A-Ah ... Iya juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.36,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Uh, his name is Ende,}Eng, dia namanya Ende.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:25.96,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{and I met him when I went to \Nbuy everyone's engagement rings.}Ketemu pas tempo hari beli \Ncincin tunangan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.32,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{He was trying to buy some things}Sebelumnya dia memakai ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.23,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{with a strange coin he claimed \Nhe used to be able to use,}... koin aneh untuk membeli makanan, tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:35.67,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{but the shopkeeper rejected \Nthe coin, so I paid for him.}ditolak oleh pemilik kedai, \Njadi aku yang membayarkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:39.73,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{He said he wanted to work since \Nhe'd be in trouble without money,}Dia pengin kerja karena \Nrepot kalau tidak punya uang, jadi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:41.73,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{so I led him to the guild.}kuantar ke guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.01,Flashback,Ende,0,0,0,,{I managed to register, thanks to your help.}Berkatmu, aku berhasil mendaftar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:45.33,Flashback,Ende,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Touya.}Makasih, Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.96,Flashback,Ende,0,0,0,,{I hope we meet again somewhere.}Semoga bisa ketemu lagi di suatu tempat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:54.05,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I never thought we'd meet again \Nin the middle of the desert, though.}Tak kusangka bakal ketemu lagi \Ndi tengah gurun begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:59.57,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{The currency from here is still being used?}Memang sekarang masih ada \Norang yang pakai mata uang ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:02.24,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Cesca, you recognize this money?}Cesca, kamu tahu mata uang ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.69,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{I'm shocked.}Aku kaget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.38,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{That is a Partheno silver coin.}Itu koin perak Partheno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:10.73,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{It was first minted 5,284 years ago.}Pertama kali dibuat \Npada 5.284 tahun yang lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.78,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:15.93,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{It doesn't look like such a long \Ntime has passed for this coin.}Tapi sangat tak terlihat setua itu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:20.11,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{So he possessed a 5,000-year-old coin,}Membawa koin 5.000 tahun lalu ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:23.93,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{and defeated a monster we \Ncouldn't scratch in a single blow.}... dan mengalahkan monster yang \Ntak bisa kita kalahkan dengan satu serangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.69,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{He also knew about that monster in detail,}Terlebih, tahu tentang \Nmonster itu secara detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.38,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{and wore a muffler even in this heat.}Pakai syal di cuaca panas begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.36,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{He's just bursting with suspiciousness.}Sungguh mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:34.32,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I don't think that last one \Nhas much to do with anything,}Meski yang terakhir itu tak \Nterlalu ada hubungannya, tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.78,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{but I guess the fact remains \Nthat he is suspicious.}yah, tapi tetap mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.33,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{Ende...}Ende.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.35,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{Just who is he, then?}Sebenarnya dia siapa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:43.87,Main,Elze,0,0,0,,{Hey, that crystalline monster...}Hei, monster kristal itu ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.99,Main,Elze,0,0,0,,{He called it a Phrase, right?}... disebut Phrase, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.96,Main,Elze,0,0,0,,{What exactly was that?}Ujung-ujungnya, apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.75,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{You know something, don't you, Touya?}Touya-san, kamu tahu sesuatu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:56.40,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Actually, I received a message \Nfrom the professor.}Sebenarnya, sebelumnya \Naku terima pesan dari profesor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.14,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{The same Professor Regina Babylon \Nthat created this Garden and Cesca.}Dari profesor Regina Babylon \Nyang ciptakan taman dan Cesca.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:04.63,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Apparently, the professor was using \Na device to look into the future,}Ternyata profesor punya perangkat \Nuntuk melihat masa depan ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:07.36,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{and observing our lives from the past.}... dan mengamati \Nkehidupan kita dari masa lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:08.81,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{But then,}Tapi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:15.74,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{one day, the Phrase suddenly appeared \Nout of nowhere, and Partheno collapsed.}suatu hari, Phrase mendadak muncul entah dari mana \Ndan menghancurkan tempat profesor, Partheno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:18.29,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{The professor said she was \Nable to predict the events}Setelahnya, profesor meramal \Nperistiwa yang mengarah ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:22.04,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{leading to the world's \Ndestruction by the Phrase,}... pada kehancuran \Ndunia yang disebabkan Phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.43,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{but for some reason, \Nthe world wasn't destroyed.}Tapi entah kenapa, dunia tidak jadi hancur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:31.16,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{She had no idea why, but at a certain point, \Nthe Phrase just disappeared from this world.}Entah apa alasannya, tapi suatu hari, \Npara Phrase akan lenyap dari dunia, katanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.49,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{What?}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:36.23,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Why did you keep something \Nthat important from us?}Kenapa kamu sembunyikan \Nhal seberharga itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:40.27,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Well, I was planning to tell all \Nof you about it eventually...}Ah, tidak. Aku memang \Nberniat memberitahu kalian, kok ....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.83,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{An invasion of thousands of Phrases...}Invasi ribuan Phrase ....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:46.16,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{So that's what wiped out \Nthe ancient civilization.}Jadi itu penyebab \Nmusnahnya peradaban kuno, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:50.30,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Though, despite there being so \Nmany of them 5,000 years ago,}Tapi, padahal 5.000 tahun \Nyang lalu jumlahnya sebanyak itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.74,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{there's hardly any eyewitness \Ninformation about them in this era.}tapi saat ini hampir \Ntak ada informasi mengenai itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.63,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Yet now they have begun appearing again.}Lalu sekarang mulai muncul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.24,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{What exactly is going on?}Apa maksudnya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:00.35,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Ende did say that}Ende bilang ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:04.50,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{the barrier that keeps foreign things \Nfrom entering this world was fraying,}... ini karena Penghalang Dunia yang melindungi \Nagar benda asing tidak masuk telah retak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:08.76,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{and that the Phrase from earlier \Nhad probably slipped through there.}Dan yang tadi itu \Nmungkin yang lolos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.56,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Cesca.}Cesca.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:15.58,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Did mankind not fight \Nthe Phrase 5,000 years ago?}Apa 5.000 tahun lalu umat manusia \Ntidak bertarung melawan Phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:19.93,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{No, the battles were rather dire, \Nbut they did fight back.}Tidak. Meski daya bertarungnya \Nburuk, tapi mereka tetap melawannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:24.57,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{The professor even developed decisive \Nweapons for use against the Phrase,}Profesor juga sudah kembangkan \Nsenjata tempur untuk lawan Phrase, tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:29.26,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{but by the time they were complete, \Nthere wasn't a single Phrase left.}saat sudah jadi, Phrase langsung \Nhilang tanpa satu pun tersisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.40,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Decisive weapons?}Senjata tempur?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:35.74,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{The professor created Frame Gears, \Npilotable humanoid combat weapons.}Senjata tempur humanoid ciptaan profesor\N yang dapat dipiloti, Frame Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.77,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Pilotable humanoid combat weapons?!}Senjata tempur humanoid \Nyang dapat dipiloti?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:42.21,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{The professor created things like that, too?!}Profesor menciptakan \Nyang begituan juga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:44.20,Main,Elze,0,0,0,,{What happened to them after that?}Terus setelahnya 'gimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:47.79,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{If I recall correctly, they were \Nstored in the Hangar of Babylon.}Kalau tidak salah \Ndisimpan di Hanggar Babylon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:51.79,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Which means that if the ruins we're \Nheading toward teleport us to the Hangar,}Berarti kalau kita teleportasi \Nke reruntuhan di Hanggar,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:54.34,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{we'll be able to obtain them?!}kita bisa mendapatkannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:55.17,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:57.36,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Huh? Oh, man!}Wah, gile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.72,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I'm getting a little... no, }{\i1}{really}{\i0}{ excited!}Jadi agak ... Tidak, deg-degan banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:03.64,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{Master, we've arrived at our destination.}Master, kita sudah \Nsampai di tempat tujuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:07.91,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{There's nothing here...}Tidak ada apa-apa, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:21.49,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Whirl forth, Wind! A Tempestuous \NWhirlwind, Cyclone Storm!}Pusaran angin berubah \Nmenjadi badai ricuh, Cyclone Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.41,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{It was buried in a place like this?}Ternyata ada di sini, toh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.84,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{How do we get this open?}Gimana cara bukanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.51,Main,Yumina,0,0,0,,{Touya!}Touya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.34,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Gate.}Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:49.95,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Huh? My magic isn't activating?}Lo? Sihirku tidak aktif.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.12,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Am I trapped in here?}Terjebak, nih?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:54.86,Main,Kohaku,0,0,0,,{Are you okay, Master?!}Tuan tidak apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:55.98,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Kohaku?}Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.40,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I'm fine. It was harmless.}Ah, aku tidak apa. Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.99,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{There's a teleportation circle inside.}Di dalam ada lingkaran teleportasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:04.67,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I'm going to try going in, so tell \Neveryone not to worry about me.}Aku akan cek dulu, jadi sampaikan \Npada yang lain supaya jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:07.37,Main,Kohaku,0,0,0,,{All right. Be careful.}Baiklah, hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.71,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I guess I can't get out unless \NI use the teleportation circle.}Tidak bisa keluar kalau tidak \Npakai lingkaran teleportasi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.26,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.35,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I hope it's the Hangar.}Semoga Hanggar, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.65,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Stop right there!}Berhenti di situ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.50,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Welcome to the Workshop of Babylon.}Selamat datang di Lokakarya Babylon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:52.41,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{I am the administration terminal \Nfor this place, High Rosetta.}Aku pengurus di sini, High Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:55.46,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{I would be grateful if \Nyou would call me Rosetta.}Panggil aku Rosetta saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:58.17,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{The Workshop, huh?}Lokakarya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:01.28,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{The hub of the Workshop is up ahead.}Di depan sana ialah pusat Lokakarya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:05.89,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Currently, entry is forbidden \Nto all but the compatible one.}Saat ini, selain orang \Nyang pantas dilarang masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:10.23,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Well, I have been deemed \Ncompatible by Cesca.}Aku sudah diakui sebagai orang \Nyang pantas oleh Cesca, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.04,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Cesca?}Cesca?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.21,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{You mean Francesca?}Maksudnya Francesca?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:18.29,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{I see. So you have already \Nobtained the Garden.}Begitu. Berarti kamu \Nsudah jadi pengurus Taman, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.44,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{That will make this much quicker.}Jadi cepat, deh, kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:25.45,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{I will now test you to determine if you \Nare qualified to be the compatible one!}Biar kuuji untuk menentukan \Napa kamu orang yang pantas atau bukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:28.15,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Test me? What are you going to do?}Uji? Apa yang mau diuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:33.29,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Guess the color of my panties \Nwithout moving a step from there!}Tebak warna kancutku \Ntanpa bergerak dari sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.79,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{You moron!}Bego, ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.44,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Seriously, what was that professor thinking?!}Serius, profesor itu mikir apaan, dah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.96,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Hey, what did I tell you? \NYou can't move from there.}Ah, sudah kubilang, 'kan, \Ntidak boleh bergerak?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.72,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{What, then? Are you telling \Nme to flip up your skirt?}Terus 'gimana? \NDisuruh nyingkap rokmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:44.55,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{You moron!}Bego, ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:48.95,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{If you can pull it off without moving \Nfrom there, that would also be fine!}Selama bisa melakukannya tanpa bergerak \Ndari sana, kamu boleh lakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.26,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{However, you can only answer once!}Tapi, kamu hanya bisa jawab sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.14,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Your time limit is five minutes!}Batas waktunya lima menit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:56.01,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Why are you so into this?!}Kenapa seantusias itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:58.75,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Go on, what color are they?}Nah, tebak apa warnanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:02.11,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I hate playing into your hands \Nlike this, but I'll do it!}Aku benci meladenimu, tapi baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:06.32,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Blow forth, Wind! Rising \NWhirlwind, Cool Wind!}Embusan Angin! \NTarian Puting Beliung, Cool Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.83,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?!}A-Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:20.46,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{This skirt turns away Wind magic.}Sihir angin tidak mempan pada rok ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.69,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{In that case...}Kalau begitu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:25.89,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Burn forth, Fire! Breath \Nof Flame, Fire Breath!}Membaralah, Api! \NEmbusan Api, Fire Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:31.64,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{What?!}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:35.10,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{It also turns away Fire magic, \Njust as it does Wind.}Sama seperti sihir angin, sihir \Napi juga tidak mempan pada rok ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:37.50,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{What's with that ultimate skirt?!}Rok terbaik macam apa itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.59,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{It's uselessly high-spec!}Spek tinggi yang sia-sia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.24,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Don't go getting cocky, though.}Jangan sombong dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:45.07,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{If you make me get serious, I can \Npeek at your panties whenever I want!}Kalau serius, aku bisa \Nintip kancutmu kapan pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:49.73,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{At this point, I'll just send my vision \Nunder her skirt and peek at them directly!}Kalau begini, aku harus lihat \Nke bawah roknya dan ngintip langsung!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:51.45,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Long Sense!}Long Sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.54,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Now, what color are they?}Nah, apa warnanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:03.80,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Colorless... Transparent...}Tak berwarna ... Transparan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.86,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{That's correct!}Betul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.78,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{I now recognize you as compatible,}Kamu diakui sebagai orang yang pantas ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:12.12,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{and as of this moment, Unit #27, \Ncode name "High Rosetta,"}... dan mulai sekarang, \NUnit #27, kode nama "High Rosetta" ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:14.56,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{will be transferred to your command!}... akan menuruti perintahmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.78,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Master, are you all right?}Master tidak apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:20.06,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah...}I-I-Iya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.02,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Is that so? Moving on, then.}Begitu, ya. Ya, sudah, lanjut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:25.49,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.65,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Registration complete.}Pendaftaran selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.97,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Genetic information recorded.}DNA berhasil direkam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.91,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Ownership of the Workshop \Nis now transferred to Master.}Mulai sekarang, kepemilikan \NLokakarya dialihkan ke Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:40.46,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{Oh, for crying out loud... I'll get her for this.}Ah ... tidak tahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:46.13,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Are you truly all right now?}Benaran tidak apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.13,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:50.02,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Then I shall show you the Workshop.}Kalau begitu, biar \Nkuantar keliling Lokakarya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:17:02.00,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Is this whole building just \Nan assembly of tiny cubes?}Jangan-jangan bangunan ini \Nterdiri dari kumpulan kubus kecil?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:07.92,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{What is this?}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.88,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{This is the Workshop.}Ini Lokakarya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:20.06,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{It is an all-purpose factory that can create\Nany manufacturing apparatus you imagine,}Pabrik serbaguna yang bisa membuat \Nalat manufaktur dalam imajinasi ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:24.04,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{and any work spaces needed \Nto support production.}... dan ruang kerja \Nuntuk mendukung produksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.48,Main,Youya,0,0,0,,{I see.}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:29.46,Main,Youya,0,0,0,,{So it can manipulate the minuscule \Nblocks that compose this very building}Jadi hanya dengan \Nmemanipulasi kubus kecil ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:32.93,Main,Youya,0,0,0,,{into any manner of tool or device?}aku bisa membuat berbagai \Nalat atau komponen, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:37.35,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{The only ones able to manipulate the \NWorkshop are myself and you, Master.}Orang yang bisa mengoperasikan \NLokakarya hanya aku dan Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:40.30,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Also, if you have a product \Nto serve as the original,}Lalu kalau ada barang aslinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:42.93,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{it's possible to reproduce it here.}bisa juga disalin di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:47.19,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Provided that you have all the \Ncomponent materials, of course.}Cuman, asal punya semua bahannya, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:53.77,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't have much need of this place \Nsince I can make things with Modeling,}Karena aku punya Modeling untuk buat sesuatu, \Njadi kurasa tidak terlalu diperlukan, sih, tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:57.74,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{but it's a different story if it \Ncan mass-produce what I make.}lain cerita kalau bisa menyalin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.58,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Can you reproduce this?}Bisa menyalin ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:01.74,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{For the materials...}Bahannya ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.84,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Use mythril.}... pakai mithril.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.47,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Of course.}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.34,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Scan.}Scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:13.37,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Copy.}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:19.89,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{It's fast!}Cepatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.65,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{You can also do this...}Bisa juga ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:30.65,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{to freely alter the design.}... bebas mengubah desainnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:39.29,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Blade Mode.}Blade Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:43.25,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I guess it can't copy Program along with it.}Ah, tidak bisa menyalin \Nsampai Program-nya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:46.44,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Well, that just means I need \Nto reinstate Program on it.}Yah, mungkin tinggal \Npindahkan Program-nya saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.87,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{If you will a certain number to be copied,}Kalau mengatur jumlah salinannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:51.63,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{it will continue production automatically.}nanti bisa lanjut \Nproduksi secara otomatis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.91,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I see. That's convenient.}Begitu. Praktis ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:55.30,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{This can earn money.}... dan bisa jadi uang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:59.43,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Though this makes it more \Nof a factory than a workshop.}Tapi, kalau begini lebih mirip \Npabrik dibanding lokakarya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.83,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah! Rosetta,}Oh, iya, Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:06.92,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{there was something created to fight \Nthe Phrase, right? Cesca mentioned it.}Kata Cesca ada senjata yang \Ndibuat untuk melawan Phrase, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:09.29,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{You mean the Frame Gears, yes?}Frame Gear, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.29,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Those certainly were created here.}Itu memang dibuat di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:15.20,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{I helped the professor build them.}Aku juga membantu profesor membuatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.84,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I knew it.}Ternyata benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.04,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{So they were developed in the Workshop,}Diproduksi di Lokakarya ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:22.89,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{and the completed ones were \Nlater stored in the Hangar?}... lalu yang sudah jadi \Ndisimpan di Hanggar, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.54,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{She could have just left them here...}Padahal tinggal disimpan di sini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.74,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Rosetta, can you create those Frame Gears?}Kamu bisa buat Frame Gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.84,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{That's impossible for me.}Kalau membuat, sih, tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:31.58,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:35.19,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{At present, the most I can \Ncreate is their equipment.}Saat ini, yang bisa kubuat itu peralatannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.26,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{I don't have their blueprints.}Tidak punya cetak birunya, pula.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.18,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Though the blueprints \Nmight be in the Storehouse.}Yah, mungkin ada di Gudang, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.91,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I see.}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.68,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Then we either need to find the Hangar,}Berarti harus cari di Hanggar ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:46.71,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{or find the Storehouse and \Nhave Rosetta build them.}... atau cari di Gudang \Nlalu memintamu membuatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:49.83,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Either way, there's nothing \Nwe can do at present.}Mau 'gimana pun \Ntak ada cara lain, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.80,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I guess I'll get everyone here for now.}Yang jelas, kupanggil yang lain dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.30,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Cesca probably wants to see you, too.}Cesca juga pasti \Npengin ketemu sama kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:56.70,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{Great! I'm looking forward to it!}Iya, aku menantikannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.74,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{The Workshop, huh?}Lokakarya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.04,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{That makes me kind of irritated.}Entah kenapa aku merasa kesal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:10.66,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{This is far more useful than the Garden, \Nwhich serves no purpose on its own.}Ini jauh lebih berguna daripada Taman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.97,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{My Garden has been Master's mental support}Taman telah jadi tempat \NMaster untuk tenangkan hati ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:18.51,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{by being a healing garden that provides \Npeace of mind and a space to refresh.}... dan tempat untuk segarkan tubuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:20.30,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{Your misconception is severe.}Kesalahpahaman juga ada batasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.18,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Setting that aside!}Kesampingkan soal itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:25.16,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Is it possible to rejoin the\N Garden and the Workshop?}Kita bisa gabungkan \NTaman dengan Lokakarya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.72,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{Yes. Now that ownership has \Nbeen transferred to Master,}Iya. Selama kepemilikan \Ntelah dialihkan ke Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.46,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{I believe that would be for the best.}maka itu lebih baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:35.31,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{I've lowered the strength of the barrier, \Nso it will be possible to link with the Garden.}Level penghalang sudah diturunkan, \Njadi sangat mungkin bergabung dengan Taman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:38.24,Main,Rosetta,0,0,0,,{We can control the Garden from here, as well.}Kita juga bisa kendalikan Taman dari sini, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:41.24,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{What shall we do, Master?}Mau bagaimana, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.07,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Have the Garden return to Belfast.}Kembalikan Taman ke Belfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.81,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Then have the Workshop \Nhead to Belfast, as well.}Lokakarya pun pindahkan ke Belfast juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.61,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{We'll do the docking there.}Gabungkan di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.07,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{Docking...}Gabung ....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:51.46,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.49,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{Sounds naughty.}Kedengarannya mesum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:55.33,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Just go do it already!}Sudah, cepat lakukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.17,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{My sincere apologies!}Mohon maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:03.39,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{I was unaware you were engaged to the \Nprincess! Please have mercy upon me!}Kami tidak tahu bahwa \NAnda tunangannya Tuan Putri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:06.89,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Hey, stop, stop! You're taking it too far!}Hentikan, hentikan! Berlebihan, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:08.67,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{No, no, no!}Tidak, tidak, tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:13.06,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Cecile has told me what \Na wonderful man you are.}Kami dengar dari Nona Cecile \Nbetapa hebatnya diri Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:16.24,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Cecile-san, you said something \Nyou shouldn't have, didn't you?}Kamu bilang hal yang \Ntidak perlu, dah, Cecile-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:20.06,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{At any rate, please don't \Nworry about it so much.}Yang jelas, tolong \Njangan terlalu dirisaukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:23.50,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Also, I'm not exactly a noble,}Terus, aku juga bukan bangsawan, jadi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:26.16,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{so you don't have to force yourself \Nto speak so politely, okay?}tidak usah memaksakan diri bicara formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.63,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Really?}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:29.36,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Then I'll take you up on that.}Kalau begitu, akan kuturuti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.61,Main,Logan,0,0,0,,{Hey, now, are you sure?}Hei, hei, yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:35.00,Main,Rebbecca,0,0,0,,{He said so himself. It should be fine.}Dia yang bilang sendiri. \NPasti bukan masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:37.65,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{So what will you all do from now on?}Jadi, setelah ini kalian mau 'gimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:41.52,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I imagine the three of you can earn \Na living working for the guild, but...}Kalian bertiga bisa cari \Nuang dengan kerja di guild, sih ....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.34,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{You mean the girls, right?}Maksudnya mereka, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:49.27,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{They don't have any special skills,}Mereka tidak punya keahlian khusus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:51.73,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{and they can't exactly fight, either.}Tidak punya kekuatan bertarung juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.90,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{Would you be willing to let them stay here}Sampai dapat kerjaan di kota,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.90,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,{until they find work in this city?}apa mereka \Nboleh tinggal di sini dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:22:00.66,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Sure, that part is fine.}Yah, tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:02.66,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{But work, huh?}Kerja, ya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:04.93,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{Could I have them mass-produce \Nsomething at the Workshop?}Produksi sesuatu di Lokakarya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:08.07,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{No, I want to keep the Workshop a secret,}Ah, tidak. Aku ingin \Nmerahasiakan soal Lokakarya, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:11.77,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{and it would be better to ask a \Nprofessional if I'm trading something.}Kalau berdagang, \Nmending serahkan pada ahlinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:14.15,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{So they need some other kind of work...}Berarti pekerjaan selain itu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:19.04,Italics,Touya,0,0,0,,{What should I do, I wonder?}Nah, 'gimana, ya?
